column5: If you haven't got on a team yet and still want to, please go to the tourney area and read the rules and sign up. I've cleared out all the names there so we know who has a team and who doesn't. If you were putting your name in while I was deleting everything, please replay to that thread again. We will draft anotehr round as soon as we have a few names in there.
